    ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu2.resource.OperationOutcome.Issue.getDetailsElement()

    Use QuantityDt.getUnitElement() - Quantity.units was renamed to Quantity.unit in DSTU2

    Use OperationOutcome.Issue.setDetails(String) instead - OperationOutcome.details was renamed to OperationOutcome.diagnostics in DSTU2 and a new OperationOutcome.details codeableconcept element was introduced
    ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu2.composite.QuantityDt.setUnits(String)
    Use QuantityDt.setUnit(String) instead - Quantity.units was renamed to Quantity.unit in DSTU2
